WILD symbol is present on all reels.
The BONUS symbol is present on reels 2, 3, and 4.
Hit 3x           to trigger the FREE SPINS FEATURE.
SUPER RESPIN RULES
Hit two or more full stacks of           anywhere on the reels to trigger the SUPER RESPIN FEATURE.
When the SUPER RESPIN FEATURE is triggered the game pays for regular winning combinations, after which only the full stacks of           remain on the reels.
The round starts with 3 respins. During the round, only            symbols are spinning. Every time a new           hits it remains on the reels and one more respin is awarded.
When no more respins are left, all win combinations with           are added together and paid.

If at the end of the SUPER RESPIN FEATURE 14            symbols are on screen, the 
MAJOR JACKPOT is awarded instead of win lines. The MAJOR JACKPOT is fixed at 375x total bet.

If during the SUPER RESPIN FEATURE 15           hit, the feature ends immediately and the 
GRAND JACKPOT is awarded instead of win lines. The GRAND JACKPOT is fixed at 500x total bet.
If the FREE SPINS FEATURE has been awarded by the same spin that awarded the SUPER RESPIN FEATURE, the FREE SPINS FEATURE will be played after the SUPER RESPIN FEATURE is over.
FREE SPINS RULES
The BONUS symbol is present on reels 2, 3, and 4.
Hit 3x           to trigger the FREE SPINS FEATURE.
User is awarded 10 free spins.

During the FREE SPINS ROUND, all           symbols are WILD and substitute for all symbols.
         pays with the wild paytable
Special reels are in play during the FREE SPINS ROUND.
The SUPER RESPIN FEATURE cannot be triggered during the FREE SPINS ROUND.           symbol is not present on the reels during the FREE SPINS ROUND and the feature cannot be retriggered.

Symbol WILD je prtomn na vetkch valcoch.
Symbol BONUS je prtomn na vetkch valcoch 2, 3 a 4.

Zasiahnite 3x           , aby ste spustili ZNAKY PRETOEN
ZDARMA.
PRAVIDL SUPER RESPIN

Zasiahnite dva alebo viac plne pridanch symbolov           kdekovek na valcoch, aby sa spustil ZNAK SUPER
RESPIN.

Ke je ZNAK SUPER RESPIN spusten, hra vyplat pravideln vhern kombincie, po ktorch na valcoch zostane
len plne pridan           .

Kolo zana 3 optovnmi pretoeniami. Poas kola sa pretaj iba symboly           . Zakadm, ke je zasiahnut
nov symbol           , zostane na valcoch a ste odmenen jednm alm optovnm pretoenm.

Ke u nezostali iadne alie optovn pretoenia, s pridan a vyplaten vetky vhern kombincie so
symbolom           .

Ak s na konci ZNAKU SUPER RESPIN symboly 14           na obrazovke, udeuje sa namiesto vhernch lni HLAVN
JACKPOT. HLAVN JACKPOT je fixn pri hodnote 375x celkovej stvky.

Ak je poas ZNAKU SUPER RESPIN zasiahnut symbol 15           , znak okamite skon a vy ste odmenen VEKM
JACKPOTOM namiesto vhernch lni. VEK JACKPOT je fixn pri hodnote 500x hlavnej stvky.

Ak bol ZNAK PRETOENIA ZDARMA odmenen rovnakm pretoenm, ktor odmenilo ZNAK SUPER RESPIN, budete
hra so ZNAKOM PRETOENIA ZDARMA potom, o sa ukon ZNAK SUPER RESPIN.
PRAVIDL PRETOEN ZDARMA
Symbol BONUS je prtomn na vetkch valcoch 2, 3 a 4.
Zasiahnite 3x           , aby ste spustili ZNAKY PRETOEN ZDARMA.
Uvate je odmenen 10 pretoeniami zdarma.

Poas KOLA PRETOEN ZDARMA s vetky symboly            WILD a nahrdzaj vetky symboly.
Symbol            je vyplcan tabukou vhier WILD.
Poas KOLA PRETOEN ZDARMA s v hre pecilne valce.

ZNAK SUPER RESPIN neme by spusten poas KOLA PRETOEN ZDARMA. Symbol           sa poas KOLA
PRETOEN ZDARMA nenachdza na valcoch a znak neme by optovne spusten.

vhernej lnii. Vetky vhry s nsoben stvkou z lniu.
Vetky hodnoty s vyjadren ako skuton vhry v minciach.
Pri vazstve na viacerch hernch lnich s vetky vhry pridan k celkovej vhre.
Za kad lniu je vyplaten len najvyia vhra.
